<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Earlier this month the rumour mill went into overdrive when it was reported that The Bachelor's Bella Varelis had a fling with Cody Simpson.   </p>

<p>And on Tuesday, the 25-year-old marketing consultant finally revealed the truth about her relationship with the Australian musician.</p>

<p>Speaking on the podcast Life Uncut, Bella admitted she had a 'thing' with the 23-year-old heartthrob after meeting him at a bar on Valentine's Day in Sydney. </p>

<p>'We had a little bit of a sleepover!' The Bachelor's Bella Varelis has finally revealed the truth about her relationship with Cody Simpson after rumours they had a fling </p>

<p>'I might have had a thing with Cody, like one night, a very long, long, long time ago,' she said.  </p>

<p>'He bought me a rose and then slow danced with me around Mrs Sippy in Double Bay.'    </p>

<p>She then revealed that they had 'a little bit of a sleepover,' but insisted that it was only 'one night'.     </p>

<p>Fleeting romance: The reality star explained that she had a 'thing' with the Australian heartthrob (pictured) after meeting him at a bar on Valentines Day in Sydney </p>

<p>'It was like one of things where you're like, "this is really cute, who is this guy?"' she added. </p>

<p>'Literally that was it, it was just that one night - we had a little bit of a sleepover - but no that was literally it.' </p>

<p>Bella was left heartbroken after Locky Gilbert chose her arch-nemesis Irena Srbinovska, 31, in the gut-wrenching finale of The Bachelor last week. </p>

<p>Going home: Bella (left) was left heartbroken after Locky Gilbert (right) chose her arch-nemesis Irena Srbinovska, 31, in the gut-wrenching finale of The Bachelor</p>

<p>Meanwhile, Cody split from ex-girlfriend Miley Cyrus in August after ten months of dating.</p>

<p>Miley confirmed she'd split from Cody after less than a year of dating on Instagram, telling fans the pair are taking time apart to 'work on' themselves.</p>

<p>'Right now, two halves can't make a whole and we're individually just working on ourselves to become the people that we wanna be, like everybody else at this age,' she said. </p>

<p>It's over: It comes one month after Miley Cyrus (pictured) confirmed her split from Cody after less than a year of dating</p>
